  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Customer Service Officer (Education)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a Continuing Education & Training provider in the Education industry. They are looking for a Customer Service Officer to support their team in the next phase of their business. They have multiple locations across Singapore.</p><p><strong>This Customer Service Officer would be responsible for:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Deliver professional, high-quality service in a customer-facing role.</p></li><li><p>Identify and assess customer needs to ensure consistently high service levels and satisfaction.</p></li><li><p>Take ownership of customer issues and follow through to resolution efficiently within SLAs.</p></li><li><p>Contribute to continuous improvement initiatives to enhance customer support processes.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate closely with other departments to understand operational workflows and ensure a seamless client experience.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in any disciplines</li><li>Comfortable working on weekends</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No. 19C9682</p><p>EA Reg. No. R24125912 (Soon Puei Sie) </p>",
